 isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/09/americans-views-of-israelis-have-grown-increasingly-negative-but-views-of-palestinians-have-held-fairly-steady/</guid></item><item><title>美国西班牙裔对于自己的身份对他们在美国是有帮助还是有害存在分歧</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/race-and-ethnicity/2026/07/09/u-s-hispanics-are-divided-on-whether-their-identity-helps-or-hurts-them-in-america/</link><description>有人说，拉丁裔身份是优势或联系的来源，但也有人说，这与障碍和歧视有关。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 14:26:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/race-and-ethnicity/2026/07/09/u-s-hispanics-are-divided-on-whether-their-identity-helps-or-hurts-them-in-america/</guid></item><item><title>数十个国家降低能源税或采取其他政策措施应对伊朗战争</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/07/dozens-of-countries-have-lowered-energy-taxes-or-taken-other-policy-steps-in-response-to-iran-war/</link><description>为应对中东冲突，100多个国家颁布了能源政策调整，从税收调整到燃料补贴。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 01:26:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/07/dozens-of-countries-have-lowered-energy-taxes-or-taken-other-policy-steps-in-response-to-iran-war/</guid></item><item><title>6张图表了解美国石油产量和消费情况</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/07/what-to-know-about-us-oil-production-and-consumption-in-6-charts/</link><description>以下是有关美国石油生产、消费、进口和战略石油储备的六个事实。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 01:11:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/07/what-to-know-about-us-oil-production-and-consumption-in-6-charts/</guid></item><item><title>北约获得成员国高度评价</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/global/2026/07/06/nato-gets-high-marks-from-member-states/</link><description>在接受调查的 13 个成员国中，大多数国家对北约持积极态度。 37个国家对俄罗斯的看法都是负面的，大多数人对普京和泽连斯基缺乏信心。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 01:55:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/global/2026/07/06/nato-gets-high-marks-from-member-states/</guid></item><item><title>美国式民主在全球脱颖而出的 8 种方式</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/02/8-ways-that-us-style-democracy-stands-out-globally/</link><description>今年是美国庆祝《独立宣言》发表 250 周年之际，以下是其政治制度与世界其他 105 个民主国家不同的八个方面。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 01:48:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/02/8-ways-that-us-style-democracy-stands-out-globally/</guid></item><item><title>大多数美国人支持禁止 16 岁以下儿童使用社交媒体</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/01/majority-of-americans-support-banning-social-media-for-kids-under-16/</link><description>在主要人口和党派群体中，支持禁止 16 岁以下儿童使用社交媒体的美国人多于反对者。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 14:03:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/01/majority-of-americans-support-banning-social-media-for-kids-under-16/</guid></item></channel></rss>